__DESCRIPTION__

This presentation will go through what Mojolicious::Plugin::AssetPack is and what it can be used for.

The presentation includes:
* Code examples with custom preprocessor
* Tricks on how to change the asset names
* Cache issues in browsers
* How to create an example application with Mojolicious::Plugin::Bootstrap3

http://www.mojoconf.org/mojo2014/talk/5411
